structData.title: Sunny Apartment in Zurich-Oerlikon
structData.description: Bright 3.5 room apartment located near the Hallenstadion. Excellent public transport connections to the airport and city center. diverse neighborhood with many shops.

structData.title: Industrial Style Loft in Zurich West
structData.description: Trendy open-space loft in a converted factory. High ceilings, exposed concrete, and a rooftop terrace. Perfect for young creatives or a startup couple.

structData.title: Exclusive Penthouse on Zurichberg
structData.description: Top-floor residence with breathtaking views of the city and the Alps. Features a private elevator, fireplace, and a wrap-around terrace. Absolute privacy and luxury.

structData.title: Student Room in Shared Flat
structData.description: Affordable room in a lively 4-person WG in Zurich-Wiedikon. Close to bars, cafes, and nightlife. Shared kitchen and living room.

structData.title: Historic Townhouse in Niederdorf
structData.description: Live in the middle of the old town. A unique 4-story house with exposed beams and historic charm. Steps away from the Limmat river and Grossmunster.

structData.title: Modern Flat near United Nations
structData.description: Sleek and secure 2-bedroom apartment walking distance from the UN headquarters. Concierge service and gym in the building. Ideal for diplomats.

structData.title: Spacious Family Apartment in Champel
structData.description: Quiet and green neighborhood. Large 5-room apartment with a renovated kitchen and two balconies. Close to parks and top-rated schools.

structData.title: Budget Studio near Cornavin
structData.description: Small but functional studio right next to the main train station. Perfect for a commuter needing a pied-à-terre in the city center.

structData.title: Lake View Apartment in Ouchy
structData.description: Stunning 3-bedroom flat right on the lakeside promenade. Wake up to views of the French Alps across Lake Geneva. elegant parquet floors.

structData.title: Attic Apartment near Cathedral
structData.description: Charming top-floor flat with sloping ceilings in the heart of Lausanne. No elevator, but offers a fantastic view over the rooftops.

structData.title: Architectural Gem near Roche Tower
structData.description: Modern, minimalist apartment designed by a famous architect. Flooded with light, featuring high-end appliances. Walking distance to Roche campus.

structData.title: Riverfront Flat with Rhine View
structData.description: Directly on the Rhine river. Watch the swimmers in summer from your balcony. Spacious living room and classic herringbone flooring.

structData.title: Medieval Charm in Bern Old Town
structData.description: Located in a UNESCO World Heritage building. Sandstone walls, cellar storage, and view of the Zytglogge. A truly unique living experience.

structData.title: Modern Garden Apartment in Kirchenfeld
structData.description: Ground floor apartment with a large private garden in the diplomat quarter. Quiet, secure, and very prestigious neighborhood.

structData.title: Luxury Chalet in Zermatt
structData.description: Traditional wooden chalet with modern interior. Unobstructed view of the Matterhorn. Includes a sauna and ski boot heater. Available for long-term seasonal rent.

structData.title: Lake Lugano Villa with Pool
structData.description: Mediterranean style villa in Ticino. Features a lush garden with palm trees, an infinity pool, and private lake access. Feel like you are on vacation every day.

structData.title: Cozy Apartment in Old Lucerne
structData.description: Right on the Reuss river with a view of the Chapel Bridge. Historic building with modern amenities. Walkable to everything.

structData.title: Remote Cabin in Grisons
structData.description: Secluded mountain hut for nature lovers. Simple living, wood stove heating, and surrounded by forest. Accessible by 4x4 in winter.

structData.title: Commuter Friendly Flat in Olten
structData.description: Practical and newly built apartment right at the train station hub. reach Zurich, Bern, or Basel in under 30 minutes. High standard finishing.

structData.title: Design Loft in St. Gallen
structData.description: Close to the Abbey library. Open concept living in a converted textile warehouse. High ceilings and huge windows.
